sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Controller Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller
    participant NGC as Nvidia NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>via ServiceMonitor

    %% Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment
    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate InferenceService<br/>TLS client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodMonitor<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC resources<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>MR: Register model (optional)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        MR-->>Controller: Model registered
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService status
    end

    %% Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation
    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate Account<br/>TLS client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated (API key secret exists)
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>NGC: Validate NIM account<br/>Auth: API Key
        NGC-->>Controller: Account valid + model catalog
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create image pull secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Process runtime templates<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Account status<br/>with model list
    end

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Controller,Prometheus: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
    end

    %% Flow 4: Pod Mutation
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 4: Predictor Pod Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>(triggers Pod creation)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate Pod<br/>TLS client cert
        Webhook->>Webhook: Inject labels/annotations<br/>for KServe predictor
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod spec
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Create Pod with mutations
    end
